00100       dfs_client = new DfsBroker::Client(conn_manager_ptr, properties);

00102 
00103     if (!dfs_client->wait_for_connection(timeout)) {
00104       HT_ERROR("Unable to connect to DFS Broker, exiting...");
00105       exit(1);
00106     }
00107 
00108     CommitLogReaderPtr log_reader = new CommitLogReader(dfs_client, log_dir);
00109 
00110     if (block_summary) {
00111       printf("LOG %s\n", log_dir.c_str());
00112       display_log_block_summary(dfs_client, "", log_reader.get());
00113     }
00114     else
00115       display_log(dfs_client, "", log_reader.get(), has("display_values"));
00116   }
00117   catch (Exception &e) {
00118     HT_ERROR_OUT << e << HT_END;
00119     return 1;
00120   }

00166         // skip value

00180   display_log_block_summary(DfsBroker::Client *dfs_client, const String &prefix,
00181       CommitLogReader *log_reader) {
00182     CommitLogBlockInfo binfo;
00183     BlockCompressionHeaderCommitLog header;
00184 
00185     while (log_reader->next_raw_block(&binfo, &header)) {
00186 
00187       HT_ASSERT(header.check_magic(CommitLog::MAGIC_DATA));
00188 
00189       printf("%sDATA frag=\"%s\" rev=%llu start=%09llu end=%09llu ",
00190              prefix.c_str(), binfo.file_fragment, (Llu)header.get_revision(),
00191              (Llu)binfo.start_offset, (Llu)binfo.end_offset);
00192 
00193       if (binfo.error == Error::OK) {
00194         printf("ztype=\"%s\" zlen=%u len=%u\n", BlockCompressionCodec::
00195                get_compressor_name(header.get_compression_type()),
00196                header.get_data_zlength(), header.get_data_length());
00197       }
00198       else
00199         printf("%serror = \"%s\"\n", prefix.c_str(),
00200                Error::get_text(binfo.error));
00201     }
00202   }
